{"tid":417903,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"同樣都係老人家，點解三代火影廢過土影咁多？","createTime":"2017-09-29T06:10:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-29T08:08:19.000Z","uid":86587,"like":9,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"114949ae46516a24927abe424f4cbfc679d0c401","tid":417903,"uid":86587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T06:10:53.000Z","msg":"三代火影69歲，土影大野木79歲，大野木老十年。但係大野木一個塵遁可以消滅25個須佐能乎分身，廢老三代連大蛇丸都打唔贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以話年紀大實力退步只係廢老三代掩飾自己廢嘅借口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真正實力可能連中忍考試嘅寧次都打唔贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff3c551e3405ee40bccfd619005ab7465bd0b682","tid":417903,"uid":12208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T06:25:52.000Z","msg":"我一直諗緊佢係歷代（1-4）最強火影係邊到吹出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb392f110214610fa1591342279fc3976a937485","tid":417903,"uid":12252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T06:26:46.000Z","msg":"駁唔到"},{"pid":"5b9d675916aa142d1cdafef38c5ad0fbb7773a4b","tid":417903,"uid":89868,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T06:34:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我一直諗緊佢係歷代（1-4）最強火影係邊到吹出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁係因為後期火影戰斗力嚴重膨脹，好似斑咁，隨便一刀就劈開幾座山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。後期火影唔係叫忍界大戰，應該叫星球大戰。平心而論，三代反而先似返個忍者，而佢嘅能力係前期黎講又的確幾勁"},{"pid":"0736b5185ebba2af48ffbe509629af1ba5c973bb","tid":417903,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T06:36:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"15c7838ceed6ec6b06cfeeab116f1b0e2acb0e59","tid":417903,"uid":23021,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T06:37:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我一直諗緊佢係歷代（1-4）最強火影係邊到吹出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁係因為後期火影戰斗力嚴重膨脹，好似斑咁，隨便一刀就劈開幾座山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。後期火影唔係叫忍界大戰，應該叫星球大戰。平心而論，三代反而先似返個忍者，而佢嘅能力係前期黎講又的確幾勁</blockquote><br />\n作者自己鳩<br />\n又要吹到最勁<br />\n個天花版又唔set高d"},{"pid":"33c9d2d5e964d8f04665453ae13a5c66c1c0205d","tid":417903,"uid":125998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T06:39:36.000Z","msg":"CHING又追擊三代💪🏻屌得好牙"},{"pid":"2406b49e2a840fb12f44d1bbdcc4bb67a8f84c45","tid":417903,"uid":82404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T07:03:33.000Z","msg":"全盛期三代先係最勁<br />\n唔係岸本點會唔比佢咁出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36764ad144e505505394a93e5683dd4bf76dfc73","tid":417903,"uid":5190,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T07:13:42.000Z","msg":"樓主戇鳩仔黎 大家唔洗理"},{"pid":"6c8a851175232641bd035234f872ccf49a1d90fb","tid":417903,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T07:16:22.000Z","msg":"嗰陣未諗到之後會玩到咁大"},{"pid":"a6321b93afee30086ae6a32ae52787ee991343a2","tid":417903,"uid":40157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T08:05:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>全盛期三代先係最勁<br />\n唔係岸本點會唔比佢咁出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁點解穢土轉生果陣係廢老黎既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b03e9bf0455a28e71bfa7f9ed3ce2be4a8a664d9","tid":417903,"uid":82404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T08:08:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>全盛期三代先係最勁<br />\n唔係岸本點會唔比佢咁出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁點解穢土轉生果陣係廢老黎既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n應該係因為靈魂留左係死神個肚到"}]}